@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Submit CV" as SubmitCV
participant "View and Edit CV" as ViewandEditCV
participant "Answer Screening Questions" as AnswerScreeningQuestions
participant "Get Rating for CV" as GetRatingforCV
SubmitCV ->> ViewandEditCV : Submit CV for parsing and analysis
ViewandEditCV -> ViewandEditCV : View parsed CV
ViewandEditCV ->> AnswerScreeningQuestions : Proceed to screening questions
AnswerScreeningQuestions -> AnswerScreeningQuestions : Answer screening questions
AnswerScreeningQuestions ->> GetRatingforCV : Submit answers for rating
GetRatingforCV -> GetRatingforCV : Calculate CV rating
GetRatingforCV ->> SubmitCV : Update CV for re-parsing
@enduml